        <mxCell id="OzgN8v3V9l0M2NgUhT2L-20" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;autosize=1;resizable=0;" value="SendGamepalyEventToActor(GetOwnerActor(), tags, payloads)&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;// 这个动画通知执行的代码，向Actor也就是玩家控制的角色发送gameplayevent&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;/**&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt; * This function can be used to trigger an ability on the actor in question with useful payload data.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt; * NOTE: The Actor passed in must implement IAbilitySystemInterface! or else this function will silently fail to&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt; * send the event.&amp;nbsp; The actor needs the interface to find the UAbilitySystemComponent, and if the component isn&#39;t&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt; * found, the event will not be sent.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt; */&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="130" width="790" x="1615" y="520" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="OzgN8v3V9l0M2NgUhT2L-21" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;autosize=1;resizable=0;fontSize=32;" value="激活ability的方式" vertex="1">
